dcterms:description: The CSRSDD dataset consists of complex SAR images collected in GF-3 Spotlight mode with 1m resolution, featuring various ship targets annotated for detection tasks. The dataset includes images of size 1024x1024 pixels, primarily focused on port areas with significant background interference.
dcterms:title: CSRSDD (Complex SAR images Rotation Ship Detection dataset)

dcterms:creator: Lan Qing
Huang, Bin
dcterms:description: OpenSARship is a public dataset collected from Sentinel-1 images, containing ground range multi-look products and slant range single-look complex products. It includes various ship types for interpretation tasks.
dcterms:title: OpenSARship
